## Workflow Rules

### Planning
- Programs and session plans live under `.training.cto/`.
- Wait for approval before large custom programs when the user asked for analysis only (unless `-y`).

### Deletion
- NEVER delete files without explicit user permission.

### Git
- NEVER `git commit` or `git push` unless the user explicitly requests it.

### No Attribution / No Signatures
- Do not add Co-authored-by or AI signatures unless the project already requires them.
